You can manipulate living plant matter, encouraging growth and changing its shape. If you do this over an extended period these changes are permanent, and can result in otherwise impossible growth. Rapid forced growth and manipulation tends to stress the plants, and the spirits in the plant will force it to return to its original state after a short time. In general, you can quickly form vine-like structures from grass and other small plant life and given time can form more intricate and complex flora. You can accomplish this at a short distance, but the effect is enhanced if you are touching the plant.
&nbsp;
When using this aspect of your craft, gain +1 die on Skill Challenges .

You are a skilled artist and, regardless of your specialty, are skilled at drawing and sketching. Given appropriate tools you can faithfully reproduce images of things seen on your adventures, and excel at understanding complex imagery and how a piece of art was made, which could grant additional insight. Additionally, choose a specialty for your art such as painting or sculpture. When working on or analyzing anything that matches your specialty all of these effects are heightened. Finally, you always understand the meaning an artist was attempting to represent when seeing their art, even if that is not how you feel about it.
&nbsp;
When your background and skills as an artist would aid in a situation, gain +1 die on an appropriate Skill Challenge or Interaction.

You are a skilled merchant, and are unrivaled when it comes to appraising items, haggling, and bartering. Deals tend to always end up in your favor, and you excel at figuring out what others want.
&nbsp;
When your background and skills as a merchant would aid in a situation, gain +1 die on an appropriate Skill Challenge or Interaction.

You are a skilled delver, able to read and understand the dangerous Underworld. The labyrinthine tunnels, secret doors, and deadly traps are all routine for you, and you're able to navigate them better than almost anyone.
