You have studied herbs, and can identify most herbs at a glance. For those that you cannot, you at least have a general sense of their properties, and can always tell if an herb would be toxic. In addition to being able to identify herbs, you are well-versed on their properties, where they grow, and other useful details.
&nbsp;
When your background and skills as an herbalist would aid in a situation, gain +1 die on an appropriate Skill Challenge or Interaction.

You've worked on a farm, granting you a strong back and endurance. Additionally, you have a broad knowledge of plants, common livestock, what to expect with the seasons, and various other tidbits of knowledge that aid in farming. Other farmers warm to you quickly, and if you speak to them about farming for a short time they'll tend to become friendly.
&nbsp;
When your background and skills as a farmer would aid in a situation, gain +1 die on an appropriate Skill Challenge or Interaction.

